{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandatory whole life sentences for convicted murderers",
        "additional_details": "If someone kills another person the deceased doesn\u2019t have a life anymore, but the killer is often freed after serving a minimum sentence. We believe they should be in prison for the rest of their life.",
        "background": "The Government should make the required sentence for murder a whole life sentence, so the offender spends the rest of their life in prison, without the possibility of parole.",
